headline: 2 Wood Stocks in Focus Despite a Tough Industry Climate
summary: More infrastructure spending, a focus on product innovation and efficient cost management are encouraging for the Zacks Building Products - Wood industry players like WY and RYN despite a challenging macroeconomic backdrop.
